import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import { ContainerCustom, ContentBlock, ContentBlockBackground, MainContent, Section, SectionRow, ContainerCustomTokenListSections,ItemListSection, ItemSelectionSection } from '../components/base/base'
import { TokensList } from '../components/TokensList/TokensList'
import { ItemSelection } from '../components/ItemSelection/ItemSelection'

import { Title, DomainTitle } from '../typography/Title'

import { AccountButton } from '../components/account/AccountButton'

import { Form } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { DomainSelectBoxContainer } from '../components/base/base'
import { DomainTitleContainer } from '../components/base/base'


export function Tokens() {
  return (
    <MainContent>
      <ContainerCustomTokenListSections>
        <ItemListSection>
          <SectionRow>
            <DomainTitleContainer>
              <DomainTitle> Meta Portal </DomainTitle>
            </DomainTitleContainer>
            <DomainSelectBoxContainer>
              <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                <option>Meta Portal</option>
                <option value="1">Crypto Punks</option>
                <option value="2">Loot</option>
                <option value="3">Skyrim Online</option>
              </Form.Select>
            </DomainSelectBoxContainer>
     
          </SectionRow> 
          <ItemsContentBlock>
            <TokensList />
          </ItemsContentBlock>
        </ItemListSection>
        <ItemSelectionSection>
          <SectionRow>
            <SignerXp>150 XP</SignerXp>
            <AccountButton />

          </SectionRow>
          <ItemsContentBlock>
            <ItemSelection />
          </ItemsContentBlock>
        </ItemSelectionSection>
      </ContainerCustomTokenListSections>
    </MainContent>
  )
}

const ItemsContentBlock = styled(ContentBlock)`
  overflow: scroll;
`

const SignerXp = styled.p`
  font-size:18px;

`
